31
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,000
Once I make up my mind,

32
00:02:07,510 --> 00:02:09,030
I won't give up on her.

33
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,150
Nobody else

34
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,030
