45
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,960
You'll have to think

46
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,470
what you can do.

47
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:53,150
Good.

48
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,710
