to get back Sheng Mian?

58
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,560
I love her, indeed.

59
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,960
But I'll get her back decently.

60
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,200
And of course,

61
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,560
