62
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,960
We can work together

63
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,360
and trap her instead.

64
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,560
OK. We'll do it together.

65
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,400
Wen Zhao,

66
